# The AI SDK arm reads the SAME repo-root .env the Python arms use (auto-loaded
# via Node's process.loadEnvFile). Copy the repo-root .env.example, or set these.
#
# ---- OpenRouter (recommended — apples-to-apples with the other arms) --------
# The benchmarked rows use qwen/qwen3-32b through OpenRouter's Anthropic-
# compatible endpoint, reached via @ai-sdk/anthropic (authToken bearer).
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
OPENROUTER_MODEL=qwen/qwen3-32b
# Optional; defaults to https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# OPENROUTER_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# Optional attribution headers OpenRouter uses for rankings.
OPENROUTER_SITE_URL=https://github.com/sheldon904/claims-audit-agent
OPENROUTER_APP_NAME=claims-audit-agent

# Force a provider regardless of which keys are present: anthropic | openrouter
# LLM_PROVIDER=openrouter

# ---- Native Anthropic (alternative backend) --------------------------------
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5

# ---- MCP demonstration (optional) ------------------------------------------
# URL of a running sparql-mcp server (SSE). Only needed for `npm run mcp:probe`
# or `node dist/cli.js ... --mcp <url>`; the scored benchmark does not use it.
# MCP_SPARQL_URL=http://127.0.0.1:4002/sse
